# Step 1: Problem Statement & Personal Role

## Problem Statement

Shopzz is a full-stack E-Commerce web application developed to provide customers with a secure and user-friendly online shopping experience. The application enables users to browse products, search items, view detailed product information, add products to a shopping cart, place orders, and manage their profiles.

The system also provides an administrative interface where administrators can manage products, monitor orders, manage users, and analyze business performance. The application aims to simplify online shopping while ensuring security, scalability, and efficient management of business operations.

## Personal Role

As the sole developer of the Shopzz E-Commerce Application, I was responsible for:

- Frontend Development using React.js
- Backend Development using Node.js and Express.js
- Database Design using MongoDB
- JWT Authentication Implementation
- API Development
- Shopping Cart Development
- Order Management System Development
- Admin Dashboard Development
- Testing and Debugging
- Deployment and Maintenance

